  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Financing agreement foresees that the mentioned grant contract the recruitment of the 6 staff will be signed by the European Commission, through its Delegation to Nigeria and ECOWAS, with the ECOWAS Commission, following a direct award procedure.The recourse to an award of a grant without a call for proposals is justified because ECOWAS Commission is in a de facto monopoly situation to implement the actions that are targeted in the project. The grant will support the employment, for 2 year</narrative>
